    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>A flurry of magic snowballs erupts from a point you choose within range. Each creature in a 5-foot-radius sphere centered on that point must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes [[/damage 3d6 type=cold]] damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"At Higher Levels\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by [[/damage 1d6]] for each slot level above 2nd.</p></div></div>",
